{"tid":2262050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有一種關係：我喜歡你，你也喜歡我，但我們不會在一起","createTime":"2020-10-28T20:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T05:17:35.000Z","uid":261496,"like":10,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4508f1683734c57ecc32548f6a2af1ff68722b90","tid":2262050,"uid":261496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T20:05:26.000Z","msg":"有一種感情，<br />\n叫作「友達以上，戀人未滿」。<br />\n明明你們倆都深愛對方，<br />\n明明你們倆都總是爲對方著想。<br />\n明明你們倆，<br />\n看著對方的眼神，<br />\n都是那麼的疼愛、珍惜。<br />\n明明你們倆，<br />\n所有情侶的事都做過了。<br />\n明明所有人，<br />\n都認為你們充滿著曖昧情愫。<br />\n可是偏偏，<br />\n你們就是沒有在一起。<br />\n你們就是停留在那個位置。<br />\n那個「友達以上，戀人未滿」的位置。<br />\n<br />\n而人生，<br />\n總是充滿著唏噓和嘆息，<br />\n而我當中大部分的嘆息，<br />\n都是因為你。"},{"pid":"24be7fd7150aa99011e7573501168b7ff58ebc70","tid":2262050,"uid":261496,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T20:09:59.000Z","msg":"想圍下爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bd73bc0bc05fd6240f592645d484bf2e1b836d","tid":2262050,"uid":34200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T20:14:26.000Z","msg":"加油，睇開啲"},{"pid":"7d1e2d8e847498aa5af5bf7843c181eb88803582","tid":2262050,"uid":261496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28bd73bc0bc05fd6240f592645d484bf2e1b836d","tid":2262050,"uid":34200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T20:14:26.000Z","msg":"加油，睇開啲"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T20:14:56.000Z","msg":"唉，好想知點解佢唔開口"},{"pid":"0e36bdd111e60a839548bc77e2244d46e8468655","tid":2262050,"uid":47219,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7d1e2d8e847498aa5af5bf7843c181eb88803582","tid":2262050,"uid":261496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28bd73bc0bc05fd6240f592645d484bf2e1b836d","tid":2262050,"uid":34200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T20:14:26.000Z","msg":"加油，睇開啲"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T20:14:56.000Z","msg":"唉，好想知點解佢唔開口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10